5","tid":975981,"uid":159876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2134fa9e690eb9d5a247c58f9514b29f79f8a061","tid":975981,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"813864e8dac97332256aa20fa1bd3a5d23cee88f","tid":975981,"uid":87571,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T05:44:49.000Z","msg":"加咗$3真係好多wo <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今年<br />\n新巴車費加咗5%<br />\n城巴車費加左7%<br />\n港燈電費加咗7%"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T05:46:50.000Z","msg":"3 / 34.5 x 100% = 8.69%<br />\n<br />\n最低工資班友返工都唔會跨區架啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T05:48:54.000Z","msg":"有得你選擇？"},{"pid":"03887f96b41e981051d577e1fe1153e3840b460f","tid":975981,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T05:59:02.000Z","msg":"次次加得幾蚊就一班人話食飯買野又貴左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係又唔話下d仆街老闆點刻薄同吸血業主點加租<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算唔加最低工資唔通個物價同個樓價就唔升<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好景個陣就減人工炒人話共渡時艱，好景個陣加人工連通脹率都唔夠，仲有班奴隸同班僱主講好話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e4769d0f6478b83bfaf469453da4ae7f7fad67","tid":975981,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T06:04:39.000Z","msg":"其實件事係好ON<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n低層嗰堆被迫要加佢, 無論佢表現好撚差都好<br />\n但公司要睇成條大數, BUDGET到比全部人加人工既數就係咁多<br />\n依家要加最底層個堆<br />\n咁中間堆文職咪加返少D, 平返條數<br />\n<br />\n變成係office tea lady / 掃地清潔阿姐, 打劫緊文職後勤<br />\n而堆文職後勤最後係唔知自己加少左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}